album.title: Keeps Gettin' Better: A Decade of Hits

wiki.content: Keeps Gettin' Better is the first single of Christina Aguilera's new Greatest Hits album Keeps Gettin' Better: A Decade of Hits. The album was released on November 11th 2008 (In the USA, it was be released exclusively by Target). It had its official television premiere on the 2008 MTV Video Music Awards on September 7, 2008. The song was sent to radio stations on September 22, 2008. User-contributed text is available under the Creative Commons By-SA License and may also be available under the GNU FDL.
